_sText:
Well, I Started mapping only yesterday, and for my first map I think I've done pretty well. I've added a little area that should keep you relatively occupied as you try to get to it and get gunned down in the process, and a decent selection of guns as well.

The guns available in the map are:

XM1014
M4A1
M249
AWP


Getting to the AWP is easy, even though it seems blocked off. Try finding the M249 ;)
